added.title: The Prince and the Lonely Trollstress
added.description: Seeking shelter from a snowstorm, Prince Ivandoe and Bert find themselves trapped in the home of a Giant Trollstress. Bert is convinced they'll be gobbled up as part of a terrifying Troll-Feast. As it turns out, the reality is far worse! After a humiliating doll's dress-up session (during which Ivandoe becomes "Sugarplumps - The Beautiful Christmas Fairy") they are forced to join the Trollstress and her "guests" for a tense Christmas Dinner. They manage to escape but only after making sure that, for once, the misunderstood Trollstress also has herself a very merry Christmas.
